    <text type="note" xml:lang="fr" xml:id="letter-09128"> 
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <date when-custom="1790-12-14">1790 г. lе 14 Dec.</date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>
            <p>N’oubliez pas de dire au <rs ref="people.xml#pas03">compositeur</rs> que le</p>
                <p xml:lang="ru">Эх, эх, не ладно!</p>
                <p><seg xml:lang="ru">Ах не складно</seg> — du Père peut être une parodie ou doit tourner en ridicule les:</p> 
                <p xml:lang="ru">Эх, Эх,</p>
                <p>et</p>
                <p><seg xml:lang="ru">Ах</seg>,—des Enfans.
                    <note type="editorial">
                        In this note Catherine writes about her opera <title ref="works.xml#fedoul01">"Fedul s det'mi"</title> (
                    <bibl>
                        <title ref="works.xml#sobstv02">Sobstvennoruchnyia pis'ma i zapiski imperatritsy Ekateriny II k A. V. Khranovitskomu, 1783-1793</title>
                        , <biblScope unit="pp">pp. 56.</biblScope>
                    </bibl>
                    ). A.V. Khrapovitskii notes in his diary that on <date when-custom="1790-12-14">December 14</date> he handed to Catherine rewritten opera and was ordered to make the composer hurry with the composition of music (
                    <bibl>
                        <title ref="works.xml#dnevni01">Dnevnik A.V. Khranovitskogo 1782-1793</title>
                        , <biblScope unit="pp">pp. 353.</biblScope>
                    </bibl>
                        ).
                </note>
            </p>
        </body>
